Name: TrapBot
About the game: TrapBot is a dynamic 2D action hardcore platformer in an urban style. You play as a robot who is sent to a test of endurance, passing all obstacles, enemies and destroy everything you can. Peculiarities: not easy levels, hard tests, action music, many enemies and obstacles, you cannot restore life in levels
